kali> arp -a (windows)
kali> sudo arp-scan --localnet (it provides more detailed information about the local network and connected devices)
kali> nmap -sn 192.168.0.1/24 (it provides information about hosts that respond to ICMP echo requests.)

-sn => 'no port scan' 

